{"id":823,"parent_id":822,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":823,"title":"Lamentations 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Lam.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1","content":[["div",[".title","The",["br"],["span.dominant","Lamentations"],["br"],"of Jeremiah"],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","Jeremiah laments the miserable condition of Jerusalem—Jerusalem herself complains of her deep sorrow."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.1","order":"02.26.001.54578"},["b","1"],"How doth the city sit solitary,",["i","that was"],"full of people!",["i","how"],"is she become as a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"widow"],"! she",["i","that was"],"great among the nations,",["i","and"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"princess"],"among the provinces,",["i","how"],"is she become tributary!"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.2","order":"02.26.001.54579"},["b","2"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"She"],"weepeth sore in the night, and her tears",["i","are"],"on her cheeks: among all her",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"lovers"],"she hath none to",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_2c"},"comfort"],["i","her:"],"all her friends have dealt treacherously with her, they are become her enemies."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.3","order":"02.26.001.54580"},["b","3"],"Judah is gone into",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"captivity"],"because of affliction, and because of great servitude: she dwelleth among the heathen, she findeth no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"rest"],": all her persecutors overtook her between the straits."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.4","order":"02.26.001.54581"},["b","4"],"The ways of Zion do",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"mourn"],", because none come to the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"solemn"],"feasts: all her gates are desolate: her priests sigh, her virgins are afflicted, and she",["i","is"],"in bitterness."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.5","order":"02.26.001.54582"},["b","5"],"Her adversaries are the chief, her enemies prosper; for the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"afflicted"],"her for the multitude of her",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"transgressions"],": her children are gone into captivity before the enemy."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.6","order":"02.26.001.54583"},["b","6"],"And from the daughter of Zion all her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"beauty"],"is departed: her princes are become like harts",["i","that"],"find no pasture, and they are gone without strength before the pursuer."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.7","order":"02.26.001.54584"},["b","7"],"Jerusalem remembered in the days of her affliction and of her miseries all her pleasant things that she had in the days of old, when her people fell into the hand of the enemy, and none did help her: the adversaries saw her,",["i","and"],"did",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"mock"],"at her sabbaths."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.8","order":"02.26.001.54585"},["b","8"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Jerusalem"],"hath grievously sinned; therefore she is",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"removed"],": all that honoured her despise her, because they have seen her",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_8c"},"nakedness"],": yea, she sigheth, and turneth backward."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.9","order":"02.26.001.54586"},["b","9"],"Her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"filthiness"],["i","is"],"in her skirts; she remembereth not her last",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"end"],"; therefore she came down wonderfully: she had no comforter. O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", behold my affliction: for the enemy hath magnified",["i","himself."]],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.10","order":"02.26.001.54587"},["b","10"],"The adversary hath spread out his hand upon all her pleasant things: for she hath seen",["i","that"],"the heathen entered into her",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"sanctuary"],", whom thou didst command",["i","that"],"they should not enter into thy",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_10b"},"congregation"],"."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.11","order":"02.26.001.54588"},["b","11"],"All her people sigh, they seek",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"bread"],"; they have given their pleasant things for meat to relieve the soul: see, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and consider; for I am become vile."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.12","order":"02.26.001.54589"},["b","12"],"¶",["i","Is it"],"nothing to you, all ye that pass by? behold, and see if there be any sorrow like unto my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"sorrow"],", which is done unto me, wherewith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath afflicted",["i","me"],"in the day of his fierce",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"anger"],"."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.13","order":"02.26.001.54590"},["b","13"],"From above hath he sent fire into my bones, and it prevaileth against them: he hath spread a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"net"],"for my feet, he hath turned me back: he hath made me desolate",["i","and"],"faint all the day."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.14","order":"02.26.001.54591"},["b","14"],"The yoke of my transgressions is bound by his hand: they are wreathed,",["i","and"],"come up upon my neck: he hath made my strength to fall, the Lord hath delivered me into",["i","their"],"hands,",["i","from whom"],"I am not able to rise up."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.15","order":"02.26.001.54592"},["b","15"],"The Lord hath trodden under foot all my mighty",["i",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"men"]],"in the midst of me: he hath called an assembly against me to crush my young men: the Lord hath trodden the virgin, the daughter of Judah,",["i","as"],"in a winepress."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.16","order":"02.26.001.54593"},["b","16"],"For these",["i","things"],"I weep; mine eye, mine eye runneth down with water, because the comforter that should relieve my soul is far from me: my children are desolate, because the enemy prevailed."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.17","order":"02.26.001.54594"},["b","17"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"Zion"],"spreadeth forth her hands,",["i","and there is"],"none to comfort her: the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"hath commanded concerning Jacob,",["i","that"],"his adversaries",["i","should be"],"round about him: Jerusalem is as a menstruous woman among them."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.18","order":"02.26.001.54595"},["b","18"],"¶The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"is righteous; for I have rebelled against his commandment: hear, I pray you, all people, and behold my sorrow: my virgins and my young men are gone into captivity."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.19","order":"02.26.001.54596"},["b","19"],"I called for my lovers,",["i","but"],"they deceived me: my priests and mine elders gave up the ghost in the city, while they sought their meat to relieve their souls."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.20","order":"02.26.001.54597"},["b","20"],"Behold, O",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; for I",["i","am"],"in distress: my",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"bowels"],"are troubled; mine heart is turned within me; for I have grievously",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"rebelled"],": abroad the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"sword"],"bereaveth, at home",["i","there is"],"as death."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.21","order":"02.26.001.54598"},["b","21"],"They have heard that I sigh:",["i","there is"],"none to comfort me: all mine enemies have heard of my trouble; they are glad that thou hast done",["i","it:"],"thou wilt bring the day",["i","that"],"thou hast called, and they shall be like unto me."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.22","order":"02.26.001.54599"},["b","22"],"Let all their wickedness come before thee; and do unto them, as thou hast done unto me for all my transgressions: for my sighs",["i","are"],"many, and my heart",["i","is"],"faint."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.1a","order":"02.26.001.54600"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/47.8.7-9"},"Isa. 47:8 (7–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/54.5"},"54:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.1b","order":"02.26.001.54602"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezra/4.20"},"Ezra 4:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.2a","order":"02.26.001.54604"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/7.13.8-14"},"Zech. 7:13 (8–14)"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.2b","order":"02.26.001.54606"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/22.22"},"Jer. 22:22"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.14"},"30:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"2c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.2c","order":"02.26.001.54608"},["b","2c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.7.7-9"},"D&C 101:7 (7–9)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.3a","order":"02.26.001.54610"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.8.8-9"},"Isa. 3:8 (8–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/52.27"},"Jer. 52:27"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.8.8-9"},"2 Ne. 13:8 (8–9)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/15.13.13-15"},"15:13 (13–15)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.10.9-10"},"25:10 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.3b","order":"02.26.001.54612"},["b","3b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/45.3"},"Jer. 45:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.4a","order":"02.26.001.54614"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.26.16-26"},"Isa. 3:26 (16–26)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.26.16-26"},"2 Ne. 13:26 (16–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.4b","order":"02.26.001.54616"},["b","4b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.11"},"Hosea 2:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.5a","order":"02.26.001.54618"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/1.17"},"Mosiah 1:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.3"},"Hel. 12:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.5b","order":"02.26.001.54620"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.14.14-17"},"Jer. 30:14 (14–17)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/101.2"},"D&C 101:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/103.4"},"103:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/105.9.2-10"},"105:9 (2–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.6a","order":"02.26.001.54622"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.24.16-26"},"2 Ne. 13:24 (16–26)"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.7a","order":"02.26.001.54624"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/mocking"},"TG Mocking"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.8a","order":"02.26.001.54626"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/5.20.19-20"},"D&C 5:20 (19–20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.8b","order":"02.26.001.54628"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/10.30"},"Prov. 10:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"8c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.8c","order":"02.26.001.54630"},["b","8c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/16.37"},"Ezek. 16:37"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/2.10"},"Hosea 2:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.9a","order":"02.26.001.54632"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/filthiness"},"TG Filthiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.9b","order":"02.26.001.54634"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.29"},"Deut. 32:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/47.7"},"Isa. 47:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.10a","order":"02.26.001.54636"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/79.1"},"Ps. 79:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/51.51"},"Jer. 51:51"],"."],["div",{"id":"10b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.10b","order":"02.26.001.54638"},["b","10b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/church"},"TG Church"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.11a","order":"02.26.001.54640"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.1"},"Isa. 3:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.12a","order":"02.26.001.54642"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/30.15"},"Jer. 30:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.12b","order":"02.26.001.54644"},["b","12b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/13.13"},"Isa. 13:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.13a","order":"02.26.001.54646"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/17.20.13,20"},"Ezek. 17:20 (13, 20)"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.15a","order":"02.26.001.54648"},["b","15a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/8.16"},"Jer. 8:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.17a","order":"02.26.001.54650"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.31"},"Jer. 4:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.20a","order":"02.26.001.54652"},["b","20a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/4.19.19-20"},"Jer. 4:19 (19–20)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.11"},"Lam. 2:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.20b","order":"02.26.001.54654"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/12.3"},"Hel. 12:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/lam/1.20c","order":"02.26.001.54656"},["b","20c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/7.15"},"Ezek. 7:15"],"."]]}
